asset.hookText: The Power Duo™ Carpet and Hard Floor Cyclonic Vacuum (UD20125B) offers high-powered cleaning for your carpets, bare floors and beyond, without the high price. For under $50, it has every feature you need in a vacuum, from a large, easy-to-clean dirt cup to a microfiber Vac+Dust Floor Tool for bare floors and baseboards, to onboard tools for crevices and couches!
